				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm sure that this is in here somewhere, but I wanted to resurface the discussion in case things have changed. (Plus, I looked for about 30 minutes to no avail and I should really be working  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />)
