				<td colspan="2"><span>Unless of course there are multiple bards....around 40ish it is possible to fill a temp buff box with 6 useful songs, pre the AE nerf it wasn't all that likely. (multiple bard groups are actually very useful pre 50, just rare).
<br />

<br />
Now, in the unlikely event that a) you are in a multi-bard group and b) bards stacking CoD or using another AE DoT isn't useful, you might see a full song box.
<br />

<br />
A bard with self haste and amp would more likely see it than a non-bard.</span></td>
