			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>In theory you could have 26 songs on one person, if you could find 26 songs that stack and have enough bards to twist them.  In other words the number of songs affecting a person is not limited to just the short duration buff box, any more then the first six will carry over into the normal buff window if slots are available.</span></td>
